title: Who Really Won Harden-Simmons Trade?
description:
Jalen & Jacoby breakdown everything you need to know for Super Bowl Sunday, AND predict who will win Super Bowl MVP. Then Jalen explains why he knew Harden was going to Philly all along, PLUS - who will dominate the Eastern Conference once the dust settles.
